***zm_office_outbreak***
Basicaly I made this map for ZombieHorde, And Zombie Mod, its a balance map, fun to play in, and can also be used as a regular deathmatch, bombsite, there are 3 floors, secrect basement with 2 breakable walls to get out, 2 vent shafts, 1 elevtor shaft, and secrect room on the top floor
